      <h1 class="lh-title f3 mt5 dib"><a href="/">sprime</a></h1> <small class="fade">by <a href="https://sharedbox.app/?ref=sprime" target="_blank">SharedBox</a></small>

      <h2 class="lh-copy normal f4">A simple way to archive multiple Slack channels.</h2>

      <a href="/auth" class="button">Get started</a>

