        <img src="/images/hero.png">
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="lh-title f3 mt5">FAQ</h3>

    <p class="lh-copy">
      <strong>What's this?</strong>
      Sprime provides an easy way to archive multiple Slack channels at once. We created it to clean up automatically created Slack channels from services like Drift.
    </p>
    <p class="lh-copy">
      <strong>Is this safe?</strong>
      We only request Slack permission that will let us list and archive your channels. This is a one time operation so we don't also store the "access" to your account.<br>
      We are not responsible for channels you archive though. Confirm again before you click the archive button. You know how the saying about responsibility and great power goes.
    </p>
    <p class="lh-copy">
      <strong>Who is behind this?</strong>
      The same team behind <a href="https://sharedbox.app/?ref=sprime" target="_blank">SharedBox</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="lh-copy">
      <strong>How do I get in touch?</strong>
      Send a mail to support@in.sharedbox.app
    </p>
  </div>

